<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>人戏：代价 on 祝融说。</title><link>https://zhurongshuo.com/practices/season-1/persona-and-performance/</link><description>Recent content in 人戏：代价 on 祝融说。</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 15 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://zhurongshuo.com/practices/season-1/persona-and-performance/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>楔子</title><link>https://zhurongshuo.com/practices/season-1/persona-and-performance/prologue/</link><pubDate>Sat, 15 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://zhurongshuo.com/practices/season-1/persona-and-performance/prologue/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;京城的秋天，风里带着干燥的尘土味和一丝若有若无的桂花香。苏三的杂货铺就开在一条快被摩天大楼挤碎的老胡同里。铺子不大，门口挂着块歪歪扭扭的木牌，上书“测字算命，童叟无欺”。路过的人大多以为这又是个骗老头老太太退休金的神棍据点。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;苏三正用一根牙签剔着牙，看着街对面新开的咖啡馆里，一个年轻人正对着笔记本电脑奋笔疾书。那年轻人叫陈默，是个小有名气的编剧，最近却陷入了瓶颈。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>